site_name: ARK Swift Primary Academy, White City Estate

residential_units.description: Demolition of the existing buildings and redevelopment of the site to deliver a mixed use development including 132 residential units (Use Class C3) and involving; a 5 storey building comprising a school (Use Class D1) (3,209 m2 GIA), with residential units above (Use Class C3) (2,205 m2 GIA); a 5 storey building comprising a replacement Nursery (Use Class D1) (764 m2 GIA), with residential units above (Use Class C3), (1,864 m2 GIA), 7 storey building comprising a replacement adult education centre (Use Class D1) (565 m2 GIA), with residential units above (Use Class C3), (3,694 m2 GIA), an 8 storey building containing residential units (3,535 m2 GIA), (Use Class C3) with a restaurant/café unit at ground floor level (Use Class A1 and/or A3) (142m2 GIA), a 9 storey Office building with ancillary ground floor restaurant/café (Use Class B1) (12,799 m2 GIA), a two storey building with rooftop MUGA, containing the new Youth Zone (Use Class D2) (2,506 m2 GIA), servicing, blue badge parking, cycle parking and new landscaped open space, including a new square.
